{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/characters.png?t=1728683039\" />A Rat\u2019s Life: The Cat Conspiracy is a story-rich action-adventure game that blends Collect-a-Thon and Metroidvania mechanics. It aims to recapture the exciting vibe of classic Rareware games on Nintendo 64, such as Banjo-Kazooie and Conker\u2019s Bad Fur Day,  and features deep lore and adult humor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/DeepLore.png?t=1728683039\" />The game is set within a microsociety that feels vibrant and alive, thanks to a rich story, memorable characters, a fair amount of comedy and events based on a day cycle system. The most dedicated players will have the opportunity to delve intensely into the detailed story, while others may choose to stick to the essentials</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/PoultryMeeting.gif?t=1728683039\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/metroidvania.png?t=1728683039\" />Progress through a sprawling abandoned zoo, forming an interconnected world with diverse environments, as you learn and upgrade a wide range of abilities. The Metroidvania mechanics are also narrative-based, insofar as gaining favor from specific characters unlocks access to otherwise inaccessible areas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/Collectathon.png?t=1728683039\" />This game aims to recapture the vibe of classic Collect-a-Thon games from the Nintendo 64 era, in a manner that energizes both exploration and the progression of the story. A unique object based smell mechanic will help the player find the different collectibles, some of which will allow him to build surprising context based structures. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/EatingPizza.gif?t=1728683039\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/firstPersonAction.png?t=1728683039\" />Numerous in-game abilities draw inspiration from real-life rat behaviors, gamified to provide action-oriented gameplay. The rat movements are crafted to be fluid, allowing a fast-paced and dynamic exploration of the world. You\u2019ll also get to fight enemies and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Nous remercions le Conseil des arts du Canada de son soutien.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>We acknowledge the support of the Canada Council for the Arts.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/extras/CCA_RGB_colour_e_500px.png?t=1728683039\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728683039","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1728683039","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728683039","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790350/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728683039","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},